        "title": "Supply & installation of internal fire doorsets predominantly for social housing requirements",
        "description": "***All information is available from www.advantageswtenders.co.uk, project DN511937.*** Advantage South West is seeking to select, by an open competitive tendering process, companies who will be awarded a 4 year Framework (1/4/21 - 31/3/25) from which our Members will award Contracts for the supply and installation of internal fire doorsets and associated products and associated services and associated works to each Member. ASW Members are social housing providers predominantly in the south west of England. The following are current members of ASW: Abri, Coastline Housing, Cornwall Housing, East Devon District Council, Exeter City Council, Homes in Sedgemoor, LiveWest, Magna Housing Group, Mid Devon District Council, North Devon Homes, Ocean Housing, Plymouth Community Homes, Somerset West and Taunton Council, Teign Housing, Westward Housing Group. Spend on this framework will be up to £4.5m.\r\n\r\n\r\n",
